                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#iv(erso)"/><desc> print card of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1066DavidHarp"/> is pasted onto the folio. With caption <q>“David, King of Israel with his harp,” in Amharic</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#iir(ecto)"/><desc> print card of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild"/> is pasted onto the folio. Caption in Amharic and Gə‘əz: <q>“With her beloved Son, protector of the Ethiopian people, and Redeemer of the World.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#iiv(erso)"/><desc> print card of King <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1066DavidHarp"/> is pasted onto the folio. Caption in Gə‘əz: <q>“King David.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#iiir(ecto)"/><desc> print card of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild"/> is pasted onto the folio. Captions in Cyrillic</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#ivv(erso)"/><desc> print card of Sacred Heart of <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1099StMary"/> is pasted onto the folio. Caption in French: <q>“N. D. des 3 AVE MARIA. Par votre Puissance, votre Sagesse, votre Misericorde, O Marie Immaculée <gap reason="omitted"/> [illegible].”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#21v"/><desc> a bird, in pencil</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#135r"/><desc> a print card of “When Paul Met <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1084JesusChrist"/>" is pasted onto the folio. Caption is in English: <q>“When Paul Met Jesus. Lesson Material—Acts 9:1–31.  Memory Verse—I am not ashamed of the gospel.” Romans 1:16.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#135v"/><desc> a print card of <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1039Magi"/> Note at the bottom: “©Providence Lithograph Co. The World Council of Christian Education NT–A–2.”.</desc></decoNote>
